<p><strong>Results:</strong> <strong>62.5% of bloggers who publish daily reported "strong results."</strong> That number dropped to 42.5% for those publishing 2-6 times per week, 32% for weekly publishers, and just 12.8% for monthly-or-less publishers.</p>
